caption.p: Correlation between fatty acid and oil quality attributes of a) cv. Thori and b) cv. Saif-32 of safflower. Detail of the variables is given below V1: Palmitic acid, V2: Stearic acid, V3: Oleic acid, V4: Linoleic acid, V5: Linolenic Acid, V6: Ratio (C18:1/C18:3), V7: Acid value, V8: Free fatty acid, V9: Saponification number, V10: Iodine value, V11: Refractive index.
